caption.text:
Hey, pops.
I haven't had a post with you yet. I'm sorry our first post had to be in this kind of situation.
I'm sorry too I wasn't there. If only I knew I would give my everything just to be with you.
I would say I want you back but that would be a very selfish thing to say, because I know that you already are in a better place--the best place.
Just want to let you know that I'll be okay, we'll all be okay. And that I forgive you for everything you've done wrong, and I thank you very much for everything you've done right.
You be good alright? And stay healthy too.
I'll see you soon, pops. 'Till we meet again.
